title: Genius Brands International Celerbates World Premiere of New Preschool Series Rainbow Rangers With Event at Nasdaq MarketSite in New York City on November 6th

Genius Brands Internationals New Preschool Series, Rainbow Rangers, Debuts on Nickelodeons Nick Jr. in Key 3 PM Timeslot, Reaching 90 Million U.S. Television Households and Delivering 15 Million Digital Marketing Impressions on Launch
